assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Tokai Lease Co.,Ltd. manufactures, sells, and leases temporary buildings, and fixtures and fittings in Japan. The company's solutions cover flat houses, such as convenience stores, schools, support centers, plants, post offices, fire and disaster management agencies, emergency temporary housing, government buildings, police boxes, dining rooms, offices, and toilet buildings; and unit houses comprising schools, vote counting facilities, and offices. Its solutions also cover TU suspended ceiling and partition, steel baseboard, kitchen capsule, Tokai system foundation, steel canopy and waist, steel steps, and air conditioner panels; and office equipment and fixtures, such as desk chairs, storage furniture, printers, air conditioners, home appliances, outdoor and educational equipment, and others, as well as equipment for educational facilities. Tokai Lease Co.,Ltd. was founded in 1963 and is headquartered in Osaka, Japan.
